---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Hafiz
  Translator: Daniel Ladinsky
  Author: Hafiz
  ISBN: 978-0143117544
  Publisher: Penguin Books
Format: Verse
By: Hafiz
Title: How Do I Listen?
Description: February 8
---
How do I listen to others? As if everyone were my Master speaking to
me his cherished last words.

How do I listen to you? As if you were the Alpha and Omega of all
sound.
